title: Vox Machinae

notes: Starts up fine at first with horrible fps, using the WineD3D11 tweak fixes this issue and it's playable at all. On the downside that fix is causing heavy graphical artifacts in the game environment while your cockpit and enemy units appear like they should- so yeah it's okay if you can get used to it but I wouldn't recommend it.
